description:
My place is close to the Apollo, Sylvia's, and Red Rooster, Cove, Central Park and other attractions.

I have a quaint sectional, dinette table and a mini bar to make this place like home. This space is perfect for 3. Possibly 4 with additional cost.

You will have gate access and my entry door access.

I have someone in the complex that can provide you with a key.

The neighborhood is quiet and my neighbors are as well.

Close to the ABC, 456, and the 2/3. Easy access to uber and taxi cabs.
name: Cozy, Spacious One Bedroom
review: Host did everything to make my stay well.
